title: Projects
text:
library(ggplot2)

# Basic scatter plot
ggplot(data = mtcars, aes(x = wt, y = mpg)) +
  geom_point(size = .8, col="firebrick") + xlab("Vehicle Weight") +
  ylab("Miles per Gallon (MPG)") +
  theme_bw()
